divs: sighting detailsi went out in the terrace with my camera in hand & aimed it at specific areas of the sky to snap few photos . i did not see anything but my intuition was strong & i just knew i'll get something (effects of the full moon couple of nights ago i guess :-)). a total of 4 photos was taken between 6:53:14 pm - 6:54:48 pm . on the computer i've brought it out , tiny bit by bit & frame by frame . the distance must have been miles away , as it still the images are very small this time . what is most interesting & a first for me , is that on one of the close ups it looks as if there was a hole on the sky ! i've aimed the camera in the west to east\ south part of the sky & high in the sky . it's their usual flight pattern . the sky was very clear with out any cloud formations . i quickly left the area & immediately went on the computer to search the photos .
